717808f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - Academy Street
717808f-a.text:
Broadway, at and adjoining the S.E. corner of Academy Street. Also
shown is Academy Street, south side, east from and including Broadway, to
and including Vermilyea Ave. The George Washington High School appears
on the S.W. corner of Vermilyea Ave.
October 26, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
